<MudText Color="Color.Default" Class="mt-5 mb-1" Typo="Typo.h6"> Icons </MudText>
<MudText Color="Color.Default" Typo="Typo.caption"> You can disable the alert icons with the bool NoIcon set to true. </MudText>
